                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5454" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0173</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8379 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“古”配方混“新”元素——云南白药“两步走”式混合所有制改革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Old” formula mixed with “new” elements——&quot;Two step&quot; mixed ownership reform of Yunnan Baiyao</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宇恒，应颜悦，高吴杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药；国有企业；混合所有制改革；反向吸收合并</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Baiyao; state owned enterprises; mixed ownership reform; reverse absorption and merger</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">十八届三中全会以来，混合所有制经济的发展受到前所未有的关注。2015年9月，中央出台了国企改革方案，省级国企成为新一轮释放改革潜力的重点；为贯彻落实党中央混改政策，云南省政府于2016年出台了配套文件，旨在深化国资国企改革，云南白药位列其中。破旧迎新，云南白药这家中华老字号从此踏上了一段新征程，开启了混改中的“白药模式”——上市公司在其母公司进行混改后，再对母公司进行吸收合并，实现整体上市。云南白药的混改也因此成为了行业的标杆性事件。本案例在介绍了云南白药的发展历程后，重点叙述了云南白药的混改过程，以及混改完成后云南白药发生的一系列变化，旨在引导学员掌握国企混改的动因，熟悉国企混改的具体实施路径，了解混改给国企带来的诸多变化，同时进一步思考总结此次国企混改中的可借鉴经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the Third Plenary Session of the 18th CPC Central Committee, the development of mixed ownership economy has received unprecedented attention. In September 2015, the central government issued state-owned enterprise reform plan, and the provincial-level state-owned enterprises became the focus of a new round of releasing the reform potential; in order to implement the policy documents, Yunnan Province issued supporting documents to deepen the reform of state-owned enterprises in 2016, among which Yunnan Baiyao was listed. Since then, Yunnan Baiyao, a Chinese time-honored brand, has embarked on a new journey and opened the &quot;Baiyao mode&quot;, that is, the listed company absorbs and merges the parent company after its parent company completes the mixed reform, so as to realize the overall listing. Therefore, the mixed reform of has become representational in the industry. After introducing the development process, this case focuses on the mixed transformation process of Yunnan Baiyao and a series of changes after the mixed reform. The purpose is to guide students to master the motivation of the mixed reform of state-owned enterprises, to be familiar with the specific path of the mixed reform, to understand many changes brought about by the mixed reform, and to further consider and summarize the experience that can be used in the mixed reform of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
